ebp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mqd5tgkSf6NXsk44T2jGMn-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mqd5tgkSf6NXsk44T2jGMn-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mqd5tgkSf6NXsk44T2jGMn-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mqd5tgkSf6NXsk44T2jGMn-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mqd5tgkSf6NXsk44T2jGMn-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mqd5tgkSf6NXsk44T2jGMn.jpg\" alt=\"block paving with weeds\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mqd5tgkSf6NXsk44T2jGMn-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mqd5tgkSf6NXsk44T2jGMn-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mqd5tgkSf6NXsk44T2jGMn-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mqd5tgkSf6NXsk44T2jGMn-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mqd5tgkSf6NXsk44T2jGMn-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mqd5tgkSf6NXsk44T2jGMn-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mqd5tgkSf6NXsk44T2jGMn-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mqd5tgkSf6NXsk44T2jGMn-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mqd5tgkSf6NXsk44T2jGMn.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mqd5tgkSf6NXsk44T2jGMn.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp\u003eBefore and after of the block driveway\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Future / Lisa Fazzani)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe verdict? Now that I’ve discovered the Weed Sweeper, I wouldn’t be without it. Clearing my patio and paths of weeds was a job that I really didn’t look forward to doing, but now, if any weeds do appear, I can have the patio cleared in minutes.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3 id=\"section-shop-these-weed-sweeper-altern